### HTX Project API Collection

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health

### Database Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health/db

### Full Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health/full

### List Files
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/files/list

### Upload File
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./data/samples/969229.xlsx
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Get Trades
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/trades?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Trades Summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/trades/summary

### Get Deposits
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cashflow/deposits?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Withdrawals
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cashflow/withdrawals?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Transfers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cashflow/transfers?limit=10&offset=0

### Get Cashflow Summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cashflow/summary

### Get PnL Summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pnl/summary

### Get Daily PnL
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pnl/daily?limit=30

### Get PnL by Symbol
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pnl/symbols

### Get Drawdown Analysis
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pnl/drawdown
